Add `opentelemetry-instrumentation-mcp`, instrumenting client-side tool calls
(`ClientSession.call_tool`) of the Model Context Protocol (`mcp`) Python SDK,
emitting standard GenAI `execute_tool` spans (`gen_ai.*`) via
`opentelemetry-util-genai`. Requires
`OTEL_SEMCONV_STABILITY_OPT_IN=gen_ai_latest_experimental`. Transport context
propagation, `list_tools`, and the server-side `ServerSession` are follow-ups.
